    slug: 'ayrton-senna-legacy',
    title: "Ayrton Senna: The Legacy of Racing's Most Beloved Driver",
    metaTitle: 'Ayrton Senna Legacy & Impact | MC Racing Sim',
    metaDescription: 'Explore Ayrton Senna\'s extraordinary F1 career, his iconic Monaco wins, the Prost rivalry, the tragedy at Imola, and the safety reforms that followed.',
    excerpt: 'Ayrton Senna remains the most revered driver in Formula 1 history. His raw talent, fierce rivalry with Prost, and tragic death at Imola in 1994 changed motorsport forever.',
    category: 'Motorsport History',
    tags: ['Ayrton Senna', 'F1 history', 'motorsport legend', 'racing history'],
    author: { name: 'MC Racing Sim', role: 'Fort Wayne Racing Experts' },
    publishDate: '2026-02-14',
